  "description": "TROPTIONS is the proof-gated unit-of-account asset of the Troptions institutional operating infrastructure platform. Issuance, transfer, and redemption are governed by board-approved release gates and evidence-bound compliance procedures.",
  "longDescription": "Troptions is an institutional operating infrastructure platform providing trade, transaction, ledger, liquidity, education, media, real-estate, energy, and utility coordination. The TROPTIONS unit-of-account asset is issued on both the XRP Ledger (XRPL) and Stellar mainnet to support multi-rail liquidity and exchange interoperability. Issuance is performed by a cold issuer wallet under multisig control; the warm distributor wallet holds the operational supply and provides liquidity to DEX orderbooks and AMM/LP pools. All authorization is revocable and clawback-enabled to support regulatory and compliance reversals.",
